description:
Danny is joined by friend of the show Hannah Brown to recap Netflix sensations Selling Sunset! They discuss Davina's villainery, plus get into ridiculous tangents about The Hills, Suits on USA, and lots more. Danny then recaps this week's Real Housewives of Potomac, which featured Ashley's Sip and See.


RHOP Recap: 42:24ish
